OL,3,CRetiring Manx pilot completes final
OL,4,Cflight to Ronaldsway after 40-year
OL,5,Ccareer
OL,7,FA Manx Loganair pilot has flown his
OL,8,Flast ever flight, completing a career
OL,9,Fspanning over 40 years.
OL,11,FStephen Thursfield touched down at
OL,12,FRonaldsway Airport for the final time
OL,13,Fon Monday 18 March, after 14,000 hours
OL,14,Fof flying during his career.
OL,16,FHe said: 'I still feel like the new
OL,17,Fboy taking off to the skies each day,
OL,18,Fso I can't quite believe that today I
OL,19,Ftouch down at Ronaldsway Airport for
OL,20,Fthe last time.
