OL,4,Cflight to Ronaldsway after 40-year
OL,5,Ccareer
OL,7,F'Flying has been more than a career
OL,8,Ffor me and for the last 40 years, I
OL,9,Ffind myself lucky enough to say that I
OL,10,Fhave had the time of my life flying
OL,11,Fall over the UK and beyond, in so many
OL,12,Fdifferent aircraft and in such varied
OL,13,Froles.
OL,15,F'It has been an honour to help mentor
OL,16,Fnew recruits like Joe and lead our
OL,17,Flocal team on the island, and I wish
OL,18,Fthem all the best as they take over
OL,19,Fand support the people of Isle of Man
OL,20,Ffor years to come.'
