OL,7,FStephen retires as Loganair's Isle of
OL,8,FMan Base Captain aged 65, now hoping
OL,9,Fto travel around Europe on his
OL,10,Fmotorbike.
OL,12,FHe was greeted to a water canon salute
OL,13,Fon the runway, before being met by his
OL,14,Fwife Penny, and members of his family
OL,15,Fand friends.
OL,17,FAlso waiting on the runway was
OL,18,Frecently qualified Loganair first
OL,19,Fofficer Joe Haddock, who will be
OL,20,Ftaking over from Stephen.
