OL,7,FMaurice Boyle, chief operations
OL,8,Fofficer at Loganair, said: '40 years
OL,9,Fof flying ` what an achievement!
OL,11,F'Stephen is an incredible role model
OL,12,Ffor all of our new recruits and will
OL,13,Fbe missed by staff and passengers
OL,14,Falike.
OL,16,F'We wish him all the best for the
OL,17,Ffuture and thank him for his years in
OL,18,Fservice for Loganair and more
OL,19,Fgenerally across the flying community.
OL,20,FHe is an inspiration to many.'
