OL,7,FTim Crookall, Department of
OL,8,FInfrastructure Minister, said: 'We
OL,9,Fextend our heartfelt gratitude to
OL,10,FSteve for his unwavering service and
OL,11,Fdedication to the island over the
OL,12,Fyears.
OL,14,F'With certainty, we believe that his
OL,15,Fenergy and enthusiasm will continue to
OL,16,Fenrich our community and inspire those
OL,17,Ffortunate enough to know him.'
